text: Help! The Doctor Is Drowning () is a 1974 Dutch comedy movie directed by Nikolai van der Heyde and starring Jules Croiset, Martine Bijl, Willeke van Ammelrooy, Ward de Ravet, Fanny Winkler, Frans Mulder. ==Other websites== * Category:1974 comedy movies Category:Dutch comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Nikolai van der Heyde
